# DOJO OS — .gitignore
#
# If your GitHub repo is PUBLIC, config.js contains your
# Supabase anon key. Add it here to prevent accidental commits.
#
# The anon key is low-risk by design (RLS protects all data),
# but best practice is to keep it out of public version control.

